      "side": 1,
      "message": "I think this loop is now a bit confused - it seems unfortunate to have two exit points. It seems like combining with the loop condition is not easy, so I think I\u0027d be in favour of something like:\n\n```\nd :\u003d path.Clean...\nfor {\n  ...\n  parent :\u003d path.Dir(d)\n  if parent \u003d\u003d d || parent \u003d\u003d mdir {\n    break\n  }\n  d \u003d parent\n}\n```",
      "revId": "65a3cdaaf45da9a6529100f1ba9ef2302039a9bd",
      "serverId": "d5d70762-12d0-45a1-890d-524b12d3f735"
